namespace = human_fallen_empires_features_spiral_of_death

# rotating
planet_event = {
	id = human_fallen_empires_features_spiral_of_death.100
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	immediate = {
		create_ambient_object = {
			location = this
			type = human_fallen_empires_object_circle
			entity_offset_height = {
				min = -15
				max = -15
			}
			scale = 11.975
			duration = 0
			entity_face_object = root
		}
		last_created_ambient_object = {
			set_location = {
				target = event_target:human_fallen_empires_features_spiral_of_death_falling_moon_target
				distance = 0
				angle = 0
				direction = in_system
			}
		}
		event_target:human_fallen_empires_features_spiral_of_death_falling_moon = {
			set_location = {
				target = event_target:human_fallen_empires_features_spiral_of_death_falling_moon_target
				distance = 11.975
				angle = 0
				direction = in_system
			}
		}
		planet_event = {
			id = human_fallen_empires_features_spiral_of_death.101
			days = 1
		}
	}
}
